A family of four silhouetted against the lush emerald canopy of a tropical rainforest at dusk, standing on a wooden suspension bridge draped with vines. Below them, the amber eyes of nocturnal creatures begin to glow among the dense foliage—a slow loris clinging to a branch, a fishing cat prowling near a moonlit stream, and fruit bats taking flight. The scene transitions from golden afternoon light on the left to deep twilight blue on the right, capturing the magical threshold between day and night safari. Fireflies dot the shadowy undergrowth while a magnificent white tiger rests on a rocky outcrop in the middle distance. Studio Ghibli animation style with soft, dreamy watercolor textures, rich botanical detail, and that signature sense of wonder and gentle adventure.
